I"‹<h3 id="create-the-analytics-code">Create the analytics code</h3>
<ul>
  <li>Create a file called <code class="highlighter-rouge">google_analytics.html</code> in your <code class="highlighter-rouge">_includes</code> directory and paste the following code into it:</li>
</ul>

<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>
    {% if site.google_universal_analytics %}
    &lt;script&gt;
      (function(i,s,o,g,r,a,m){i['GoogleAnalyticsObject']=r;i[r]=i[r]||function(){
      (i[r].q=i[r].q||[]).push(arguments)},i[r].l=1*new Date();a=s.createElement(o),
      m=s.getElementsByTagName(o)[0];a.async=1;a.src=g;m.parentNode.insertBefore(a,m)
      })(window,document,'script','//www.google-analytics.com/analytics.js','ga');

      ga('create', '{{ site.google_universal_analytics }}', '{{ site.google_universal_analytics_cookiedomain }}');
      ga('send', 'pageview');
    &lt;/script&gt;
    {% endif %}

</code></pre></div></div>
<ul>
  <li>Add the following code to your <code class="highlighter-rouge">_includes/head.html</code> file just before <code class="highlighter-rouge">&lt;/head&gt;</code>:</li>
</ul>

<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>
{% include google_analytics.html %}

</code></pre></div></div>

<ul>
  <li>Add this code to your _config.yml</li>
</ul>

<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>google_universal_analytics: YOUR-TRACKING-ID
google_universal_analytics_cookiedomain: auto
</code></pre></div></div>
<ul>
  <li>Replace <code class="highlighter-rouge">YOUR-TRACKING-ID</code> with your actual tracking ID.</li>
</ul>
:ET